{"tid":2068781,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「月經」鋼之煉金術師vs進擊的巨人","createTime":"2020-06-18T02:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T11:11:15.000Z","uid":4574,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68c834fdb7ac25301d568c1db9a2bebfc9250e38","tid":2068781,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"鋼煉勝在劇情完滿 劇情無漏洞<br />\n同真理之門對答 <br />\n無諗到愛德華咁答<br />\n以至雲妮打破咗 <br />\n等價交換原則  都令人感動<br />\n<br />\n巨人嘅格局恢宏<br />\n淨係第一章標題已經嚟料<br />\n致二千年後的你<br />\n個結局 諫山老師一早plan好<br />\n<br />\n各國歷史都可以喺漫畫裡窺見<br />\n初時以為係人vs巨人<br />\n原來係政治嘅延伸 <br />\n人類同政權、記憶與遺忘嘅抗爭<br />\n就算呢刻封筆 <br />\n都肯定入硬 日漫史上神作<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得<br />\n鋼煉係佳作嘅典範 <br />\n話畀你聽咩係 完滿嘅作品<br />\n<br />\n而巨人就係直追<br />\n手塚 火之鳥 水平<br />\n深度可以同宮崎駿比較<br />\n<br />\n期待作者點樣收個靚尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c300f407f1ef478a31885bd5f5b35dbd2abee046","tid":2068781,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"鋼煉，每一個人物都刻劃描述得好詳盡仔細<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇睇巨人"},{"pid":"a54081f6b1b9b2d87d54543c4c8f138aaa737b37","tid":2068781,"uid":216705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"我冇野補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de0dff32437088d5578a56944ecb54b9d9c0f4f","tid":2068781,"uid":79993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:55:57.000Z","msg":"巨人一日未完都唔好咁老定將佢上神枱，近期兩套熱門嘅都半爛尾或者平平無奇咁收尾就算，e.g. 約定夢幻島，鬼滅"},{"pid":"7ef43f733befb9e00eb978363f1952f3dad5314e","tid":2068781,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"其實都唔洗再問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個答案係公認<br />\n亦都冇懸念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ae00b7a7bffe47556f65c3bf030e31a4609f3c","tid":2068781,"uid":175,"like":0,"